{"tid":2388092,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"澳洲玻璃罐公司公開表明不再從「共產中國」入貨","createTime":"2021-01-30T23:29:51.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-31T17:01:08.000Z","uid":124021,"like":172,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"42ecaa0deba0eaacdc96dcddad458601645d5628","tid":2388092,"uid":124021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-30T23:29:51.000Z","msg":"澳中關係持續惡化之際，一間澳洲玻璃密封罐（mason jar）公司向其顧客發公開信，表示它不會再從「共產中國」入貨。<br />\n<br />\n《澳大利亞人報》報道，位於新州小鎮Kempsey的Ballmason公司向客戶發電郵，表示它所有產品將只會從澳洲、美國和歐洲入貨。<br />\n<br />\n該公司表示：「身為一家公司，我們做了一項商業決定&mdash;&mdash;將優先購入澳洲貨，如果沒有的話便會購入歐洲和美國貨。<span class=\"red\">只要有高質素的替代品，我們正盡量淘汰共產中國(CCP)製造的產品。」</span><br />\n<br />\n「我們那些中國製產品存貨，一般是由澳洲、歐洲或美國擁有的企業，在持有生產許可下製造。」<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hJAqUxQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhJAqUxQ.jpg&h=74487b7f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f7b76848ff8dd8ed46095f0451e89fa4366ad97f","tid":2388092,"uid":124021,"like":12,"dislike":2,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-30T23:30:19.000Z","msg":"自從去年初澳洲推動國際對新冠病毒起源作調查以來，澳中關係一直劍拔弩張。<br />\n<br />\n澳洲新任貿易部長鄧肯（Dan Tehan）日前表示，他已去信中國新任商務部長王文濤，尋求緩解目前緊張局勢的機會，但一直未有回音。<br />\n中國此前已對澳洲多種進口產品實施貿易限制，包括葡萄酒、農產品和煤炭等。"},{"pid":"8b090d58a9e818e8bcba8b721bf0ac1f829dbeb1","tid":2388092,"uid":279326,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-30T23:59:51.000Z","msg":"想去澳洲<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/36.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c4201e983f8d7ef7ac327d585b4c8b12d88c6ce","tid":2388092,"uid":88737,"like":23,"dislike":2,"score":21,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-31T01:11:23.000Z","msg":"澳洲都敢企硬，美國反而要縮出賣晒其他盟友<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"10bd7962423642301754583e9aab1f224688254b","tid":2388092,"uid":35087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-31T01:45:02.000Z","msg":"正"},{"pid":"086a11efeb9d32aabac2016b3da532275fa41a4f","tid":2388092,"uid":65747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-31T01:46:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"26e9c4d74e72887e6bb5ab1feaab6fd708884d5e","tid":2388092,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-31T01:47:09.000Z","msg":"CCP<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"04cc8c34ec0855d9d708cfa78af69a17d8db599d","tid":2388092,"uid":70301,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-31T01:49:46.000Z","msg":"make Australia great again！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee24f6e1bb4fc9b3ee1b87d7f93b996909f9ce19","tid":2388092,"uid":44454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-31T01:51:40.000Z","msg":"最緊要帶起潮流"},{"pid":"c5e3cba06c03ff5ffbe11ae98d04044c2e07f3f3","tid":2388092,"uid":251732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-31T01:52:46.000Z","msg":"真係希望佢喺香港搵代理畀我哋幫襯佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b71d3835fd88a9d6f0092fcdea9b64a876898661","tid":2388092,"uid":49329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-31T02:01:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc0f55fce8c19d57